Handle Tasks Definitions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Handle - Commands pertaining to Handle itself

handle.command						send a command the interpreter
handle.exit 							begin shutdown
handle.update							update the Handle code
handle.checkup						check for handle update

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Network - Commands pertaining to network communication to and from the UI

network.job								a job update request from the client
network.screen						a full screen update request from the client
network.version						a Handle version update request from the client
netowrk.lineup						a line update to the client from the server

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Server - Commands Pertainging to the control of the Bukkit server

server.start							start the bukkit server
server.stop								stop the bukkit server
server.restart						restart the bukkit server

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


